{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "93726139-21c3-4e91-b7a4-7321c222e31b", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/93726139-21c3-4e91-b7a4-7321c222e31b@3.pkg/1772597491817/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597492162", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/93726139-21c3-4e91-b7a4-7321c222e31b@3.pkg/1772597491817/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597492162"}, "identifier": "93726139-21c3-4e91-b7a4-7321c222e31b", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>D:延迟退休可以增加劳动力有效供给，有利于缓解人口老龄化压力，从而促进经济发展，故D符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>A:我国仍需要长期坚持计划生育的基本国策，故A说法错误;</p>\n\n<p>B:应该是调整计划生育政策，刺激提升低生育水平，有利于减轻老龄化影响，故B说法错误;</p>\n\n<p>C:延迟退休可缓解养老金压力，但“提升养老金保障水平”并非直接解决老龄化根源问题，故C说法错误;</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025山东烟台中考真题）自2025年1月1日起，我国逐步将男职工的法定退休年龄从原60周岁延迟到63周岁，将女职工的法定退休年龄从原50周岁、55周岁，分别延迟到55周岁、58周岁。对此，以下关于延迟退休可能带来的连锁影响，推导合理的是（&nbsp; ）​</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025山东烟台中考真题）自2025年1月1日起，我国逐步将男职工的法定退休年龄从原60周岁延迟到63周岁，将女职工的法定退休年龄从原50周岁、55周岁，分别延迟到55周岁、58周岁。对此，以下关于延迟退休可能带来的连锁影响，推导合理的是（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/93726139-21c3-4e91-b7a4-7321c222e31b@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754970210095", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associabl